titleStmt.title: An Account of the men of war (not including privateers), taken from the French since the beginning of the war, (declared the 7th of May, 1689) to the 1st of October, 1695

notesStmt.note: Place and date of publication from Wing.
Reproduction of original in Huntington Library.

An account of the men of war and vessels of the Navy Royal of England (not including privateers) taken by the French, and otherwise lost, since the beginning of the war (declar'd the 7th of May, 1689) to the 1st of October, 1695: p. 1-3.
